{"tid":2258693,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平樹敵太多 搞「一世極權」","createTime":"2020-10-26T08:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T11:47:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1925dcba9353d3d7cf4a8ce79412ba3571eef6","tid":2258693,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201026/XV4LJNGVF5BQDACZZPK4FLRKDQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201026%2FXV4LJNGVF5BQDACZZPK4FLRKDQ%2F&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oIRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=0916ddd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201026%2FXV4LJNGVF5BQDACZZPK4FLRKDQ%2F&h=1f7fe573\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201026/XV4LJNGVF5BQDACZZPK4FLRKDQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n習近平樹敵太多 搞「一世極權」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jkQ1mi7ynM-jxSiDkGJKHtLh1K4=/1648x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CNPS3NJHCVDT5LMECBFH4N3CSU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjkQ1mi7ynM-jxSiDkGJKHtLh1K4%3D%2F1648x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCNPS3NJHCVDT5LMECBFH4N3CSU.jpg&h=d3f3a8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習近平（中）推動2035遠景，有指欲為「一世獨裁」鋪路。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n背景<br />\n<br />\n2035年遠景目標源起於十九大報告，內容涵蓋了經濟、國防、科技、教育、文化等領域，要提早完成鄧小平預計在本世紀中葉才能達致的目標。各領域遠景目標早前都有公佈直至2035年藍圖。教育要成為「學習大國、人力資源強國和人才強國」；深圳要城市綜合經濟競爭力世界領先，成為「創新創業創意之都」等；科技則要在2035年建成「全球領先的創新共同體」。某種程度上說，中國規劃已不再是五年規劃，「十四五」亦只是為2035目標作部署。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：五中全會今揭幕定2035目標  習硬推雙循環不歸路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析<br />\n<br />\n胡星斗稱，現時尚未有具體指標可供評論，例如平均每萬人應有多少病床、醫藥負擔率在30%以下等。但他認為以中國現時制度很難實現這些民生改善，需要在治理、經濟、教育、醫。。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"8e388e1775d2727d27e7658f8b1170eaaff87506","tid":2258693,"uid":295442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:59:26.000Z","msg":"快啲FC<br />\nYouTube 有傳佢出事！<br />\n中咗"},{"pid":"b34f483c9be73da81dbb7dfb1d1c1eb434096b0c","tid":2258693,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:45:00.000Z","msg":"家陣最想佢死,其實係中共黨員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢同美國作對, 令到中共黨員 無得再移民去美國, 仲唔憎死佢"},{"pid":"6906b040d5bd7bb2f5e214704ff1314f6327a2de","tid":2258693,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:47:26.000Z","msg":"紅二代：喂我地搞共產黨挾錢走咋喎，你咁癲真係想做皇帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}